---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="LinkedIn Video - Kenny Raymond">

  <!-- Title -->
  <section class="px-6 md:px-16 lg:px-24 pt-20 md:pt-24 pb-6 md:pb-10">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-semibold text-white leading-tight">
      LinkedIn Video
    </h1>
  </section>

  <!-- Hero image -->
  <section class="px-6 md:px-16 lg:px-24">
    <img
      src="/Videohero.png"
      alt="LinkedIn Video hero"
      class="w-full h-auto rounded-2xl"
    />
  </section>

  <!-- Overview -->
  <section class="px-6 md:px-16 lg:px-24 py-14 md:py-20">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-white mb-6">Overview</h2>
    <p class="text-white text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6 max-w-3xl">
      Video creation and consumption on LinkedIn was growing rapidly year over year, creating a major opportunity for the company. We launched a dedicated video tab that gained traction and quickly became one of LinkedIn's fastest-growing surfaces.
    </p>
    <p class="text-white text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
      I led the end-to-end design, shaping the vision, defining the experience, and driving fast execution while maintaining a high quality bar.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- GIF -->
  <section class="flex justify-center px-6 py-10 md:py-16">
    <img
      src="/tabcompressed.gif"
      alt="LinkedIn Video tab interface"
      class="w-72 md:w-80 h-auto rounded-2xl"
    />
  </section>

  <!-- Impact -->
  <section class="px-6 md:px-16 lg:px-24 py-14 md:py-20">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-white mb-6">Impact</h2>
    <p class="text-white text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6 max-w-3xl">
      Since launching the new video experience, watch time has increased significantly and major creators from other platforms have started sharing video on LinkedIn.
    </p>
    <p class="text-white text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
      The success of the team's work elevated the initiative into a top company priority and strategic investment for LinkedIn. The work also received external recognition, with coverage in <a href="https://techcrunch.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="underline">TechCrunch</a>, <a href="https://axios.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="underline">Axios</a>, and <a href="https://www.techradar.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="underline">TechRadar</a>.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Mockup images -->
  <section class="px-6 md:px-16 lg:px-24 py-10 md:py-14">
    <div class="bg-neutral-200 rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 md:gap-8 items-center justify-center">
      <img
        src="/video mock left.png"
        alt="LinkedIn Video mockup — feed view"
        class="w-full md:w-1/2 h-auto"
      />
      <img
        src="/video mock right.png"
        alt="LinkedIn Video mockup — profile view"
        class="w-full md:w-1/2 h-auto"
      />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Back link -->
  <section class="flex justify-center py-16 md:py-24">
    <a href="/work" class="text-white text-base md:text-lg font-medium">
      ← More Projects
    </a>
  </section>

</Layout>
